title: Spherex - MiiiX (2014 Summer Mixtape)
description:
Spherex - MiiiX (2014 Summer Mixtape) [Various Artists]

All tracks 320Kbps MP3

26 Individual Mashups
1 Continuous Mix
1 Promo Video

Explore an alternate way of hearing popular music currently on most radio! The mad scientist of mashups is back with this Summer DJ mixtape, perfect for when you want a bit more push and complexity to familiar tunes. For this mix, all songs were put up against neurofunk, glitch hop, dubstep and trap beats. All individual mashup tracks are included, so you can even add these to your own mixes! The continuous mix is included, but does not contain all the tracks for this release.. Enjoy!!!
ALL CONTENT USED belongs to its creators listed, I merely matched key and tempo to these songs and edited them together for DJ use..

WEB: http://spherex.midwestmassive.com/spherex-miiix-summer-2014-dj-mashup-mixtape/
